{"tid":111193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際舊聞]  英蝻亞幫性侵案6被告判刑　庭上呼真主偉大","createTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T08:08:43.000Z","uid":23479,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f35361234edee0c0ac79db478a0094c295787bf","tid":111193,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"02月03日(五)<br />\n<br />\n英國南約克郡羅瑟勒姆鎮於2014年揭發，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過去16年來有多逾1400名小童遭性侵</span></span>，警方調查後拘控<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多名南亞裔人</span></span>。案中最後6名被告周四亦被判刑合共逾80年，其中2名被告被帶離庭時，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>在庭上高呼「真主偉大」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n被判刑的6名被告年齡由32至41歲，除2人是羅瑟勒姆鎮居民外，另外2人來自諾丁漢郡，2人則來自謝菲爾郡。他們被指在1999年至2001年間，在南約克郡多次性侵兩名女童，其中一名女童自11歲起已遭各被告灌酒灌藥，趁她神智不清時強姦她，女童在2001年更因此懷孕。當時警方曾拘捕5名涉案男子，但由於受害無法認清誰人是腹中塊肉經手人，因此無人被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n直至南亞幫性侵案被揭發後，警方拘捕多人，其中6名被告終在昨日分別被判監10至20年監禁不等，合共逾80年。在之前已有多達18人，因為涉及1997年至2013年間，逾<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1400名小童遭性侵案</span></span>，被判監合共280年。"},{"pid":"e1b09f29e9f286f73927cb2527aeeb6bd152f7da","tid":111193,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"真主偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eb52c5e3c07c42935c430bacf403aac3775103","tid":111193,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/photo/bknint-20170203163621224-0203_17011_001_01b.jpg?20170203170048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170203163621224-0203_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170203170048&h=4e06510d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46d93bc7afb64a74637f778d59e8b7456058872b","tid":111193,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"當時警方曾拘捕5名涉案男子，但由於受害無法認清誰人是腹中塊肉經手人，因此無人被起訴。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255135cb5c6b39d30073b5d86c9da782244ab2a3","tid":111193,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb3b5ee74df810930c46e4d8ead572952ee76b7","tid":111193,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431d9435d3cb94105c029931bb360a36a3eb75d1","tid":111193,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"235729beec57598e6609db8a7ea3c9ac8781b027","tid":111193,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"我識d ust南亞仔好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb1cb9624ced8d0df6410798f9019322cf0eea0","tid":111193,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"蝻亞人好撚多好嘛，呢d只係唔好個班，我地要每隻蝻都去接觸先可以話人不是"},{"pid":"0e3c947d90c6588038156c91cf6651c5af218916","tid":111193,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"蝻去到世界每個角落都係病毒式存在"},{"pid":"e83263f797387f8c6012c9b9c73e4656e02493d7","tid":111193,"uid":59206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"連e d事都有左膠撐<br />\n難怪右派接管世界"},{"pid":"720e0b19c2f9ee6951dc42bee159aecaca362eb9","tid":111193,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連e d事都有左膠撐<br />\n難怪右派接管世界</blockquote><br />\n右翼幾時再抬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji